290
00:27:30,482 --> 00:27:33,818
Eh, um...

291
00:27:33,902 --> 00:27:38,114
Ah, that's right. Will Kara laugh?

292
00:27:38,198 --> 00:27:39,657
(Satoshi) So I guess that's the case.

293
00:27:39,741 --> 00:27:41,534
What a pain! (sound of tapping on table)

294
00:27:41,618 --> 00:27:43,745
- (Mamiya) Sorry - (Satoshi) Huh...

295
00:27:43,828 --> 00:27:47,665
But in that case, the president has already confirmed it before⸺

296
00:27:47,749 --> 00:27:51,044
“This is too casual, so I wanted something a little cooler.”

297
00:27:52,212 --> 00:27:55,131
So, now with the data specified by the president⸺

298
00:27:55,215 --> 00:27:57,258
