That's what you said, right? last time

302
00:28:11,064 --> 00:28:13,566
Oh, isn't that so?

303
00:28:16,694 --> 00:28:18,113
(Satoshi) Don't say it.

304
00:28:21,783 --> 00:28:23,702
I didn't say it... I didn't say it.

305
00:28:25,161 --> 00:28:27,330
(Satoshi) When did I say that? ?

306
00:28:27,414 --> 00:28:31,459
-(Mamiya) Last time... -(Satoshi) Don't say that!

307
00:28:31,543 --> 00:28:34,003
You said you wanted to see me smile!

308
00:28:34,087 --> 00:28:36,631
(Yukiya) Is this the attitude of someone in a higher position?

309
00:28:37,465 --> 00:28:42,178
Satoshi-kun, you really haven't changed.

310
00:28:43,221 --> 00:28:48,435
Always violent towards people who are weaker than themselves

311
00:28:49,561 --> 00:28:54,566
