312
00:28:57,569 --> 00:28:59,279
It's for the sake of the world

313
00:29:18,506 --> 00:29:20,341
You did it

314
00:29:20,425 --> 00:29:22,177
Thanks to Satoshi

315
00:29:22,260 --> 00:29:23,845
No no...

316
00:29:24,471 --> 00:29:26,264
-(Satoshi) Well, yes-(Erika) Hehehe...

317
00:29:26,931 --> 00:29:28,558
Are you feeling okay?

318
00:29:29,517 --> 00:29:30,393
Yeah

319
00:29:31,686 --> 00:29:36,149
I wanted to see this scene with my own eyes.

320
00:29:36,649 --> 00:29:39,194
I'm glad I made it on time

321
00:29:40,195 --> 00:29:43,990
If we join hands, we can aim even higher.

322
00:29:44,741 --> 00:29:47,202
As long as Erika is here, the world is no longer a dream.

323
00:29:47,285 --> 00:29:51,289
I'm convinced now

324
00:29:51,789 --> 00:29:53,166
happy

325
00:29:53,249 --> 00:29:54,667
laughter)

326
00:29:55,585 --> 00:29:59,088
(buzz)

327
00:30:01,716 --> 00:30:02,550
(Customer) Huh?

328
00:30:03,843 --> 00:30:05,804
-(Customer) Hey, over there... -(Customer) Huh?

329
00:30:07,472 --> 00:30:08,389
Huh?

330
00:30:10,767 --> 00:30:12,435
(Video audio: laughter)

331
00:30:13,603 --> 00:30:16,189
(Video audio: kicking sound) (Satoshi) Don't look! That's not it

332
00:30:16,731 --> 00:30:19,025
I don't have that much free time!

333
00:30:19,108 --> 00:30:20,401
(Mamiya) Like that last time...

334
00:30:20,485 --> 00:30:24,030
You said you wanted to see me smile!

335
00:30:24,531 --> 00:30:27,659
Don't make excuses and get ready! I can't use it!

336
00:30:27,742 --> 00:30:29,202
What is this...

337
00:30:31,204 --> 00:30:35,792
(Staff) No, that's good. I'm smiling. It was great!

338
00:30:40,004 --> 00:30:42,048
(Satoshi) Hey Kumaki

339
00:30:42,549 --> 00:30:43,591
yes

340
00:30:45,218 --> 00:30:49,722
(Satoshi) Hey, I was asking if you were listening!

341
00:30:49,806 --> 00:30:51,683
hey hey!

342
00:30:51,766 --> 00:30:56,813
Are you listening? Hey! Hey! Hey!

343
00:31:06,197 --> 00:31:08,408
-(Staff) Thank you for your hard work.-(Yukiya) Thank you for your hard work.

344
00:31:10,868 --> 00:31:15,623
Are you listening? Hey! Hey! Hey!

345
00:31:16,374 --> 00:31:17,709
(Kotoko) What do you mean?

346
00:31:17,792 --> 00:31:19,836
(Customer) Isn't that the president?

347
00:31:20,587 --> 00:31:23,423
(Customer) Seriously? I felt like buying it all at once.

348
00:31:23,506 --> 00:31:25,425
(Customer) I was a fan of Satoshi.

349
00:31:25,508 --> 00:31:26,634
(Satoshi) Hey!

350
00:31:30,555 --> 00:31:32,181
(Customer) I hate people like that the most.

351
00:31:35,310 --> 00:31:37,228
(Customer) It's impossible for me to hit something.

352
00:31:37,312 --> 00:31:38,771
(Customer) No, I've already hit someone.

353
00:31:40,815 --> 00:31:42,358
What's going on here? ?

354
00:31:42,442 --> 00:31:44,193
Mr. Satoshi...

355
00:31:44,277 --> 00:31:48,114
Hey, who did this? Come out!

356
00:31:48,197 --> 00:31:51,034
Hey, Kumaki? Mamiya?

357
00:31:51,117 --> 00:31:53,453
Hey!

358
00:31:54,537 --> 00:31:57,248
(Satoshi) Hey, what are you doing? What's going on? ?

359
00:31:57,332 --> 00:31:59,500
-(Satoshi) Erase it quickly! -(Kotoko) Sorry!

360
00:31:59,584 --> 00:32:04,589
(Satoshi) Hey, hey, why are you putting it back? Buy it! Hey!

361
00:32:04,672 --> 00:32:08,468
(Voice changer) This is Satoshi Ise's true identity.

362
00:32:08,551 --> 00:32:09,928
(Satoshi) Don't be silly!

363
00:32:10,511 --> 00:32:11,721
What are you doing? What's going on?

364
00:32:11,804 --> 00:32:13,514
 Erase it quickly!

365
00:32:14,349 --> 00:32:16,643
-(Kotoko) Sorry! -(Satoshi) Erase it quickly!

366
00:32:17,226 --> 00:32:20,271
-(Satoshi) Hey! Hey! - (Kotoko) Sorry, sorry.

367
00:32:20,355 --> 00:32:23,399
(Satoshi) Hey! Umm... Aah!

368
00:32:23,483 --> 00:32:27,528
Aaaaaah! It...it won't disappear!

369
00:32:27,612 --> 00:32:30,365
What is this remote control? ? Hey! Hey!

370
00:32:30,448 --> 00:32:33,493
Cheers to these two poor people

371
00:32:33,576 --> 00:32:35,953
(Satoshi) Damn it!

372
00:32:45,713 --> 00:32:48,675
Shame on the Ise Group

373
00:33:28,256 --> 00:33:30,925
Call Masayuki, I'll do something right away.

374
00:33:31,009 --> 00:33:32,301
(fuyu) yes

375
00:33:37,807 --> 00:33:38,683
(clicks tongue)

376
00:33:39,892 --> 00:33:42,395
Who did this?

377
00:33:44,772 --> 00:33:48,234
(Streaming audio: Masayuki) I am very sorry.

378
00:33:48,317 --> 00:33:52,113
(shutter sound)

379
00:33:52,780 --> 00:33:56,409
(Masayuki) Eh~ Satoshi Ise took it⸺

380
00:33:56,492 --> 00:34:02,290
Unfair behavior towards our employees will never be tolerated.

381
00:34:02,373 --> 00:34:06,669
This time, none of us are alone⸺

382
00:34:06,753 --> 00:34:09,005
What I didn't understand about this matter⸺

383
00:34:09,088 --> 00:34:12,258
I deeply apologize.

384
00:34:14,135 --> 00:34:18,806
(shutter sound)

385
00:34:18,890 --> 00:34:21,476
Also iSE Interfashion⸺

386
00:34:21,559 --> 00:34:24,228
To our loyal customers⸺

387
00:34:24,729 --> 00:34:29,358
I am sorry for making you feel uncomfortable.

388
00:34:29,442 --> 00:34:34,447
(shutter sound)

389
00:34:40,203 --> 00:34:41,287
just⸺

390
00:34:42,246 --> 00:34:47,835
Honestly, I feel like I've been betrayed... I'm filled with regret.

391
00:34:49,962 --> 00:34:51,130
(Reporter) Sorry!

392
00:34:51,714 --> 00:34:54,092
Is it true that you didn't understand?

393
00:34:54,175 --> 00:34:57,470
