(Reporter) Also, there are reports that the source of this leak is an employee.

396
00:35:01,557 --> 00:35:04,435
Can I ask you about this as well?

397
00:35:05,686 --> 00:35:06,813
Well...

398
00:35:08,689 --> 00:35:13,194
Regarding such matters, we are currently investigating...

399
00:35:13,277 --> 00:35:15,863
(Reporter) Regarding the fact that power harassment was a daily occurrence.

400
00:35:15,947 --> 00:35:17,657
Please tell me in detail

401
00:35:17,740 --> 00:35:19,951
He poured beer on an employee who made a mistake⸺

402
00:35:20,034 --> 00:35:20,993
Is it true?

403
00:35:21,077 --> 00:35:22,703
(Moderator) Sorry, I have questions for each person...

404
00:35:22,787 --> 00:35:25,331
(Reporter) Yes! Family-run business⸺

405
00:35:25,414 --> 00:35:27,333
Regarding the fact that it is seen as a problem⸺

406
00:35:27,416 --> 00:35:29,085
What do you think?

407
00:35:31,128 --> 00:35:32,213
(Masayuki) Ah...

408
00:35:34,173 --> 00:35:35,007
No, that...

409
00:35:40,805 --> 00:35:41,639
Eh, that...

410
00:35:54,402 --> 00:35:59,490
I am very sorry about this matter.

411
00:36:01,325 --> 00:36:03,536
Ise Group takes responsibility⸺

412
00:36:04,120 --> 00:36:09,041
Immediately begin providing emotional support and compensation to those affected.

413
00:36:09,125 --> 00:36:14,005
We will do our best to prevent the same thing from happening again.

414
00:36:15,381 --> 00:36:17,675
Respect diverse opinions⸺

415
00:36:18,217 --> 00:36:22,096
We hope that you will trust us more than ever⸺

416
00:36:23,181 --> 00:36:25,141
Ise Group as one⸺

417
00:36:25,224 --> 00:36:28,186
We aim to create an open workplace.

418
00:36:29,061 --> 00:36:33,524
(shutter sound)

419
00:36:36,277 --> 00:36:38,070
So this time⸺

420
00:36:39,405 --> 00:36:40,865
Rent this place⸺

421
00:36:40,948 --> 00:36:43,951
There is something I would like to report.

422
00:36:45,703 --> 00:36:50,416
This is Erika Ise, the new president of iSE Interfashion.

423
00:36:50,499 --> 00:36:52,793
(Noisy noise in the venue)

424
00:36:52,877 --> 00:36:54,253
‪♪～

425
00:36:54,337 --> 00:36:55,254
Huh?

426
00:36:55,922 --> 00:36:58,424
(Erika) I have just been invited to introduce you⸺

427
00:36:58,507 --> 00:37:02,803
My name is Erika Ise, and I am the new president of iSE Interfashion.

428
00:37:02,887 --> 00:37:07,099
First, regarding the matter of former president Satoshi Ise⸺

429
00:37:07,183 --> 00:37:09,226
We apologize for the inconvenience⸺

430
00:37:09,977 --> 00:37:11,520
I'm sorry

431
00:37:13,940 --> 00:37:16,150
I deeply regret the actions of the former president⸺

432
00:37:16,233 --> 00:37:20,154
Aiming to create a company that never disappoints our customers' expectations⸺

433
00:37:20,237 --> 00:37:23,157
iSE Interfashion will be reborn!

434
00:37:29,121 --> 00:37:30,790
(Yukiya) These guys...

435
00:37:31,415 --> 00:37:33,668
Can I keep it alive like this?

436
00:37:34,627 --> 00:37:35,836
Everyone...

437
00:37:37,046 --> 00:37:39,507
I will never forgive you

438
00:37:44,095 --> 00:37:47,223
(Fuyu) This is a letter from Erika-sama.

439
00:37:54,647 --> 00:37:56,649
‪～♪

440
00:38:05,449 --> 00:38:06,784
What is this?

441
00:38:16,002 --> 00:38:17,586
 (Yukiya) How to erase you⸺

442
00:38:17,670 --> 00:38:19,130
It's very simple

443
00:38:19,213 --> 00:38:20,965
(Kyoko) Please don't let me down.

444
00:38:21,048 --> 00:38:22,091
(Reo) It still feels like a dream

445
00:38:22,174 --> 00:38:24,302
People I have been in contact with recently⸺

446
00:38:24,385 --> 00:38:25,761
Isn't it dangerous?

447
00:38:25,845 --> 00:38:27,471
 (Yukiya) Erase from that house
